TO-DO website
This is a simple to-do list web application built using HTML, CSS, and JavaScript. It allows users to add, mark as complete, and delete tasks, with the ability to save the list locally.


Features:
User-friendly interface
Local storage support to save the to-do list
Ability to add, mark as complete, and delete tasks
Optional themes or customization



Technologies Used:
HTML for the structure and content
CSS for styling the user interface
JavaScript for the interactive functionality, such as adding and managing tasks
